description: Generates sample findings of types specified by the list of finding types. If --NULL' is specified for findingTypes, the API generates sample findings of all supported finding types.

parameters.name: DetectorId
parameters.description: The ID of the detector for which you need to create sample findings. To find the detectorId in the current Region, see the Settings page in the GuardDuty console, or run the ListDetectors API.

parameters.name: FindingTypes
parameters.description: The types of sample findings to generate. (string) ---
